        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p>
          RentEase is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy
          outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the
          steps we take to protect your data.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name, contact details (email, phone number)</li>
          <li>Property details (location, rent, amenities)</li>
          <li>Payment information (if applicable)</li>
          <li>Device and browsing data (IP address, browser type)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your information is used to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
          <li>Communicate with you regarding your listings or inquiries</li>
          <li>Process payments and manage transactions</li>
          <li>Ensure the security and integrity of our platform</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>We may share your information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Payment service providers for processing transactions</li>
          <li>Third-party service providers assisting us with operations</li>
          <li>
            Law enforcement or government authorities when required by law
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your
          personal data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is
          completely secure.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information</li>
          <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be
          reflected on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
          at:
          <br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:contact@rentease.com">contact@rentease.com</a
          ><br />
          Phone: +91 9949169887
        </p>

        <p>@RentEase. All rights reserved.</p>
